01:13:40,944 --> 01:13:41,778
Lilin Nazar

776
01:13:41,862 --> 01:13:42,696
Alice Menyelamat

777
01:13:50,871 --> 01:13:52,080
Tuan-tuan.

778
01:13:53,749 --> 01:13:57,252
Tolong awasi lelaki ini.

779
01:13:58,253 --> 01:14:00,338
Namanya Gerald Fenn.

780
01:14:00,464 --> 01:14:02,257
Dia suka bawa masalah.

781
01:14:02,382 --> 01:14:06,261
Kita tak mahu kejadian tak diingini. Okey?

782
01:14:06,386 --> 01:14:07,387
-Ya, tuan.
-Faham.

783
01:14:07,512 --> 01:14:08,513
Terima kasih.

784
