799
01:16:04,755 --> 01:16:07,090
Aku menyerahkan kepada Mu hari ini,

800
01:16:07,215 --> 01:16:12,345
mataku, telingaku, mulutku, hatiku,

801
01:16:12,471 --> 01:16:15,140
